      "note": "Accepted risk: TOTP QR-code SVG generation on the enrollment page. The QR payload composes (1) the TOTP seed read from Rails.cache (server-generated, never user-controllable) and (2) Current.user.username, which is a citext column constrained by User validations and only writable by the authenticated owner. RQRCode emits a fixed SVG structure (path elements + fixed attributes); the username only appears inside the QR matrix bitmap encoding, not as raw markup. The page is mandatory-2FA-gated and reachable only by the enrolling user. Acceptable."
    },
