      "note": "Defense-in-depth: Pito::AssetsRoot.path runs cleanpath + containment and raises Pito::AssetsRoot::Error on any attempt to escape the composites directory (../, absolute paths, symlink tricks, etc.). The controller rescues that error and returns head(:not_found), so traversal payloads never reach send_file. The .jpg suffix is hard-coded and the directory is locked to \"composites\". Acceptable false-positive."
