      "note": "Intentional: stash_intended_url must NOT fire on HEAD requests. HEAD is a cache validation probe (e.g., from Turbo, Link prefetch, monitoring), not a navigation event. Stashing a HEAD path as the post-login redirect would send the user to a URL they never intended to visit. The strict `request.get?` check (which returns false for HEAD) is correct."
